titleStmt.title: Newes from Francfort, concerning the election of the most mighty Emperor Matthias the first of that name who was elected and crowned in Francfort, in Iune last, anno. 1612. Translated out of Dutch into English.

publicationStmt.publisher: Printed [by George Eld] for Henry Holland, and are to be sold at his shop in Iuy lane, at the signe of the Holy-bush,

notesStmt.note: The first leaf verso contains "The Emperors stile and titles, as he was proclaimed in Francfort: the 13. of Iune 1612".
Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
